Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveNollywood actress Uche Ogbodo has urged single ladies to be patient and and not give up on finding a good man.
Sharing a photo of herself on Monday, the role interpreter encouraged women to work on themselves too.
Uche Ogbodo’s post read, “Ladies be patient , there are still good men out there, your own will find you . Work on being the best version of yourself first.”
